T02D1725:91b-1: au dre t'a r'a m'u la tantra sto tra n'a ma /
T02D1725:91b-3: sgrol ma khro mo la rtsa ba'i sngags kyis bstod pa /
T02D1725:91b-4: jo mo byin rlabs can la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D1725:91b-5: phyag 'tshal ral pa gcig 'chang khro mo ni //
T02D1725:91b-6: mi ro dmar po'i steng na brkyang bskum bzhugs //
T02D1725:91b-7: rgyas pa'i lha mo stag dang sbrul gyis brgyan //
T02D1725:91b-8: shin tu khros pas gad rgyangs cher sgrogs pa //
T02D1725:91b-9: g-yas pas ral gri mthing gser rtse la me 'bar zhing //
T02D1725:91b-10: 'og ma gcod byed gri gug rab tu 'phyar //
T02D1725:91b-11: g-yon gyi dang po autpala rab rgyas shing /
T02D1725:91b-12: 'og ma thod pa skra bcas raktas bkang //
T02D1725:91b-13: ral ba'i thor cog dbul rab tu mdzes //
T02D1725:91b-14: spyan gsum sa gsum gzigs pas dri med tshul //
T02D1725:91b-15: mgo bo'i thod phreng skam rlon spel mas mdzes //
T02D1725:91b-16: de lta'i gzugs ni gzhan min bdag nyid do //
T02D1725:91b-17: dpal ral pa gcig ma'i rtsa ba'i sngags don 'gyur
T02D1725:91b-18: du bsgyur ba'i bstod pa tshigs su bcad pa rkang
